  "description": {
    "zh": "嗨，进来聊聊。我今天需要把线路布置好，还得按计划储备大量的电力，尤其是还要考虑到电网的持续负荷。但这不是现在的问题，给我找些烟来，我需要在不分心的情况下努力工作直至结束。我知道，吸烟在折我的寿，但是谁会在乎呢。总之，给我20包烟，最好是不同种类的。哦对了，一定要是没拆封的那种，所以你得自己找，不要去找别人买。我等着你回来。",
    "en": "Hello, come here a minute. I need to lay the wiring today, and plan for high power capacity, especially considering the continuous load on the grid. But that’s not the issue now, bring me some cigarettes. I want to work it hard until it’s done, and don't want to get distracted with searching. I know, smoking’s going to kill me. But is it really important though? Well, anyway, I need around 20 packs, preferably different ones. Oh, and make sure you get the new sealed ones, so look for them yourself. Was good seeing you."
  },
